                                <h2>VEX Robotics Competition team</h2>
                                <p>The VEX Robotics Competition is a robotics competition for elementary
                                    through university students. It is a subset of VEX Robotics, which is in
                                    turn a subset of Innovation First International.</p>
                                <p>The Conestoga Robotics
                                    Team participates in the High School division of the competitions we visit.
                                    Every year a new challenge is given and teams must create a robot that best
                                    suits the tasks at hand. With more than 20,000 teams from 50 countries
                                    playing in over 1,700 competitions worldwide, VRC is one of the fastest
                                    growing robotics challenges.</p>
